snippet.title: Maps & Themes I Feature Highlights Ep 7 I Cities: Skylines II
snippet.description:
New landscapes, new challenges, endless limits! Are you ready to think big cause the world just got a whole lot bigger in Cities: Skylines II.🗺️

Which map will you build your dream city on? Let's find out in the newest Feature Highlight, all about Maps & Themes!

Footage captured In-Game is not final and might change in time for release.

Pre-Order Cities: Skylines II NOW!
